				<td colspan="2"><span>I assumed he meant what do you use when you are slowing, hasting, CCing, and pulling ;o)
<br />

<br />
When I am not slowing, then I take out RoT and toss in BBB.  When it lights up, I swap out Lull for Amp.  Then I sing Amp, HoS the mob, and BARD NUKE!!   I really havent found much use for DA song in normal exp situations.  I know it helps with aggro management, but I rarely run into times when my party members cant manage aggro.  If they do get aggro, most can hold thier own while the tank gets aggro back, or I can CC the mobs.  If they cant manage aggro, and I cant CC, then that is why I have Fade, so I can drag corpses back to a safe area to rez ;o)</span></td>
